    Title: Mânava-dharma-sâstra
    Locus: II 96
Tags:
  - Discernment-Truth=Knowledge=The Excellence of Wisdom
---
Those (organs) attached to sensual objects cannot be curbed so much by
non-indulgence as ever by knowledge.
